gs be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the length of a man\u2019s prayer and the brevity of his sermon is a sign of his understanding. Lengthen the prayer and shorten the sermon. Verily, some eloquence is charming.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 869 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15799,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/23\/attend-sermon-quietly\/","url_meta":{"origin":4202,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Jumuah: Minor sins forgiven until next Friday","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever performs ablution in the best manner, comes to Friday prayer, and listens while remaining quiet, his\u00a0sins will be forgiven until the next Friday and an additional three days, but whoever plays with pebbles has behaved\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15815,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/23\/special-moment-friday-dua\/","url_meta":{"origin":4202,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jumuah: Special moment for Friday supplications","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Burdah reported: Abdullah ibn Umar said to me, \u201cHave you heard anything narrated by your father from the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, about the special moment on Friday?\u201d I said, \u201cYes. I heard him narrate that the Messenger of Allah said, 'It is the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3213,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/05\/16\/no-talking-jumuah-khutbah\/","url_meta":{"origin":4202,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Khutbah: Not allowed to speak during Friday Sermon","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf you tell your companion to be quiet on Friday while the Imam is speaking, you have spoken improperly.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 892, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 851 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim Al-Nawawi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28148,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/prophet-prays-after-friday-in-his-house\/","url_meta":{"origin":4202,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Friday: The Prophet prays after Friday in his house","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would not pray after Friday prayer until he had departed and thus would pray in his house. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 895, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 88